                text = "*(It is you. Older. Hollowed, not by cruelty, but by *certainty* — the worst hollowing there is.)* Don't be afraid. I'm not here to kill you. Killing you would only start it over, and I am so very tired of starting over. I'm here to do you the one kindness no one ever did me: to spare you the long road. I have walked it. Every step. Every era you're about to bleed through, I bled through first.",
