                text = "The Unmade's offer is real, and it is not a trick, and that is the horror of it. Pull the first thread — say yes — and Maerin lives. Aldric's daughter never dies, never walls, the grief never gathers. Everyone you have lost, un-lost. I know, because I refused it, age after age, exactly as you are about to — and every refusal seeded the sorrow larger, until it pulled back a soul filed under nothing, and that soul was me, and that soul was *you*, and here we are again, you and I, having this conversation we have always had.",
